{"tid":1533504,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"02 Impreza 2.5RS 行咗41萬 買唔買得過？","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T10:39:28.000Z","uid":211923,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3d48fe2d429a4a0e209df7c7a9f5decc7c00ec3d","tid":1533504,"uid":211923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:39:48.000Z","msg":"如題，喺澳洲<br />\n<br />\n標價AUD$2900，有少少甩漆，司機位門鎖從入面壞咗，同埋懸掛都好似要整<br />\n<br />\n不過睇相內籠同座椅都幾乾淨，同埋賣家勤做維修，里數似係high way mileage，因為賣家住得有少少偏遠<br />\n<br />\n所以想請問各位巴打咁嘅情況買唔買得過？之前見到有另一架幾靚仔01年放咗一日即刻俾人買咗，但呢架放咗起碼兩個禮拜都未有人買，係咪真係之後會有好多嘢要整？？架車會唔會已經操到好傷 多損耗？？<br />\n<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ea67099ce7c5930929c0762558528b31eafeca","tid":1533504,"uid":211923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:41:35.000Z","msg":"02年"},{"pid":"e6603c4ccbad631e494dcc10a10f8f5800ec5397","tid":1533504,"uid":259345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:41:41.000Z","msg":"入黎了解真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［整合］聽日早上7點 光復大埔何郭佩珍中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6710aa48486121a9fd2d7693366583543ae2f16a","tid":1533504,"uid":289649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http